Class AbstractQueryResultParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.rdf4j.query.resultio.AbstractQueryResultParser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    QueryResultParser
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractSPARQLJSONParser, AbstractSPARQLXMLParser, AbstractTupleQueryResultParser, BooleanTextParser, QueryResultParserBase

    public abstract class AbstractQueryResultParser
extends Object
implements QueryResultParser
    Base class for QueryResultParsers offering common functionality for query result parsers.
